ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
PrecisApproval to enter into a TAX ADMINISTRATION AGREEMENT with the TLICHO FIRST NATION pursuant to which the Government of Canada will collect, within the territory of this First Nation, a value-added tax on goods and services, similar to the federal GST.
